*rspec-1.2.6 (03 May 2009)

  03 May 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rspec-1.2.6.ebuild:
  Version bump with several enhancements and a few bug fixes.

  24 Apr 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rspec-1.2.4:
  Add ruby19 to USE_RUBY.

